        </item>
        <item>
            <title>再見「紅色的跑車」 WhatsApp 一級方程式 Emoji 用 Mercedes-AMG 賽車配色</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/01/whatsapp-mercedes-amg/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=whatsapp-mercedes-amg</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/01/whatsapp-mercedes-amg/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 08:00:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交網絡]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mercedes AMG]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[WhatsApp]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1232741</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>過往一級方程式賽車的 emoji，都是一架「紅色的跑車」🏎。而 WhatsApp 決定為賽車 emoji 大翻新，新 emoji 將呈現 Mercedes-AMG PETRONAS F1 團隊的顏色。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232586" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1714459543_whatsapp_-694x441.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="441" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1714459543_whatsapp_-694x441.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1714459543_whatsapp_.jpg 760w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>WhatsApp 今次同 Mercedes AMG PETRONAS F1 團隊合作，新 WhatsApp 賽車表情符號現呈現黑色底，輔以青藍色的點綴。新 emoji 日前在美國紐約帝國大廈亮相。此 emoji 將會陸續向全球 WhatsApp 用户推送。另外 Mercedes-AMG 也在 WhatsApp 建立品牌頻道，提供各種資訊。</p><p>WhatsApp 自從被收購以來，Meta 一直努力維持 WhatsApp 的非廣告化立場。雖然曾有關於 WhatsApp 將引入廣告的報導，但負責人 Will Cathcart 已作出否認。Meta 通過為企業建立獨立應用與功能，成功地從這款即時通訊應用中獲利。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">we upgraded the race car emoji so you never forget we’re team <a href="https://twitter.com/MercedesAMGF1?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@mercedesamgf1</a> 🏆 <a href="https://t.co/jPI4F3BrhQ">pic.twitter.com/jPI4F3BrhQ</a></p><p>&mdash; WhatsApp (@WhatsApp) <a href="https://twitter.com/WhatsApp/status/1785066883433079173?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 29, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/whatsapp-beta-dialler-hidden-group/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 開發電話撥號器，方便用户隨時致電他人</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/26/whatsapp-ios-now-added-passkey-support/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 提升保安功能，宣佈為 iOS 程式加入 Passkey 支援</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/25/whatsapp-keep-chats-organized-with-chat-filters/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 新增對話列表篩選條件，助用家快速找到所需訊息</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/01/whatsapp-mercedes-amg/life-tech/auto/">再見「紅色的跑車」 WhatsApp 一級方程式 Emoji 用 Mercedes-AMG 賽車配色</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
